{"tid":1251080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人封Email要求增開24小時新聞台","createTime":"2019-06-22T11:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T19:28:38.000Z","uid":227929,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0c5728958193d06bcdf7ac7e7d850d9dccc22527","tid":1251080,"uid":227929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T11:01:46.000Z","msg":"見呢幾日無線新聞咁仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我相信大家除咗NowTV網上新聞台都未有代替品㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以喺呢度希望各位可以一齊send個email去香港電台同埋Viu TV到作出建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟才疏學淺，如果有更加好嘅修改版本歡迎大家喺樓下寫低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，紅色字嗰度就自己改啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nViuTV:enquiry@viu.tv<br />\n致ViuTV營運團隊<br />\n<br />\n鑑於近日無綫新聞報導不全面，散播不客觀事實，愚弄大眾。<br />\n<br />\n希望貴公司可以增設24小時新聞頻道，以確保香港新聞自由，及大眾知情權<br />\n<br />\n請有關當局處理，捍衛新聞自由。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你個名</span>上<br />\n<br />\nRTHK:ccu@rthk.hk<br />\n致香港電台營運團隊<br />\n<br />\n鑑於近日無綫新聞報導不全面，散播不客觀事實，愚弄大眾。<br />\n<br />\n希望貴公司可以增設24小時新聞頻道，又或於32台中加入新聞報道，以確保香港新聞自由，及大眾知情權<br />\n<br />\n請有關當局處理，捍衛新聞自由。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你個名</span>上"},{"pid":"3e785a7a7e7943ce0a45cf0301f4fc05f6863034","tid":1251080,"uid":227929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T11:04:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"980ae4a4683eff8b997b1240918ab235459a4b50","tid":1251080,"uid":227929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T11:05:40.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ac6328703861c437cda001b712dd80d57ca9b7","tid":1251080,"uid":157983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T11:06:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0a8b45db7b1c93f63d013c1cdfc1bfad752216e","tid":1